paragraph: Kate Price is a hammered dulcimer player and vocalist born in Salt Lake City, Utah.  She has made recordings on several labels, including Priceless Productions, Access Music, Higher Octave / Om Town, Narada Productions, and LunaVerse Music.
Price's music fuses folk music with elements of classical, jazz, and ethnic music, using instruments from around the world.
